    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The treatment of a surface to give the appearance of bronze. In printmaking, refers to printing with metallic inks.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000039621/Antreasian and Adams, Tamarind Book of Lithography (1971)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Pintura de una superficie para darle la apariencia del bronce. En impresión, se refiere a imprimir con tintas metálicas.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
